Figure 36. 
<taxonomicName box="[328,521,1255,1277]" class="Insecta" family="Phoridae" genus="Megaselia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="53" pageNumber="159" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirticrus">
